{"url": "http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2016/06/14/10-ways-to-be-a-fabulous-grandparent_n_10460336.html", "date": "2016-06-14", "content": "Your beloved adult child is about to embark on a lifelong commitment about which they understand nothing. So it\u2019s not surprising you\u2019re as alarmed for them as you would be if they were sailing the Northwest Passage in flip-flops. Whichever phrase of warning or concern springs to your lips, however, hold it in. Your child needs support, not dread.\nSo if you can\u2019t pretend you\u2019re thrilled, find something supportive to say. It will be appreciated.", "title": "10 Ways To Be A Fabulous Grandparent"}